Name: Yachu Dice
About the game: Yachu Dice! Yachu is a simplified version of the classic Yahtzee dice game with clean UI supporting 'Local Multiplayer' Roll the dice, score high and beat your friends! You can play with friends up to 4 players Yachu currently features: -high scores -number of Yachts scored -single device Multiplayer support -hosting and joining a Local Multiplayer ( LAN ) game * online multiplayer will be updated in the future
